channel.title: Should I release my 508 loading 525? ~Project Insane~
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/mybanner.png[/img][/center]
[center]Hey guys I have been working on this 508 loading 525 for a while now so I am here to show you a couple of features of what it has & you tell me if I should release or keep hosting it.
[ul][li]Working soul split with gfx[/li] [li]All working leech prayers with right gfx[/li] [li]Turmoil with working gfx & animation[/li] [li]Working pvp system *Cant farm for pvp points*[/li] [li]Pvp point shops with pvp armor weapons & customs[/li] [li]Over 35 teleports & places to go[/li] [li]Slayer tower for whips & dark bows[/li] [li]All kind of multi & non multi zones[/li] [li]No training ::master ::pure ::zerker[/li] [li]Some items are spawn able some are not[/li] [li]New bork tormented demons with right animations & mapdata[/li] [li]Quest tab you can spawn items & teleports[/li] [li]Drop parties work just go to the party room in Falador[/li] [li]Godwars = pro[/li][/ul]
[IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/godwars-1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/corporalbeast.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/bork.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/1v1pvp.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/bountyhunter.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/home.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/magebank-1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/Magicsspellbooks.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/multipvp.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/partyroom.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/pkpointrares.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/pkpointshop.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/prayerscustomsprimal.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/Questtab.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1038.photobucket.com/albums/a465/Runescapeprivateservers/Specialsturmss.jpg[/img] [/center]
